#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""check-lyrics — Tenth Hour lyric singability + AI-tell checker.

Analyzes clean lyrics against:
- Singability (line-ending vowel openness, syllable variance, opening clusters)
- Rhyme structure (per-stanza schemes)
- AI tells (manifesto blacklist patterns, modern psych language, suspect-word frequency)
- Punctuation rules (Suno-aware: no ellipses in first 1-2 lines, etc.)

Usage:
    check-lyrics path/to/lyrics.txt
    check-lyrics path/to/lyrics.txt --label "Song Name"
    check-lyrics path/to/lyrics.txt --json   # machine-readable output
"""

